Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:27.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:30.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:33.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:36.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:36.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:42.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:49.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:06.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:11.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:16.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:18.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:19.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:22.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:29.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
